def is_near_microwave(microwave: item):
    symbol near_microwave = exists dr: item : is_dining_room(dr) and inside(microwave, dr)
    return near_microwave

behavior place_milk_in_microwave(milk:item, microwave:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(milk, microwave)

behavior heat_milk(microwave: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(microwave)
        achieve is_on(microwave)

behavior __goal__():

            is_cup(cup_with_milk) and on(cup_with_milk, kitchen_counter_230)
        
        place_milk_in_microwave(cup_with_milk, microwave)
        heat_milk(microwave)
